down in the dumps...

271
00:15:04,625 --> 00:15:07,625
why not try hitting up
ol' John Titor for advice?

272
00:15:10,416 --> 00:15:13,250
In his earlier posts...
Titor did mention

273
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:14,791
that altering the past
would change the...

274
00:15:14,875 --> 00:15:18,333
