don't remember it...

288
00:15:53,166 --> 00:15:57,208
to them, it never
actually transpired.

289
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,125
Yet I remember everything...

290
00:16:01,208 --> 00:16:03,250
But how is that possible?

291
00:16:08,958 --> 00:16:10,416
Aw, balls! Nae!

292
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:11,958
