304
00:16:35,875 --> 00:16:37,125
My good Mr. Braun,
I've no idea what you're--!

305
00:16:37,208 --> 00:16:38,166
Don't lie to me!

306
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:39,666
That's my baby
girl you're eying,

307
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:41,375
so don't think you can
run your experiments

308
00:16:41,458 --> 00:16:43,291
on her up there in
that creepy lab of yours!

309
00:16:43,375 --> 00:16:45,250
How dare you
insinuate I would stoop

310
00:16:45,333 --> 00:16:46,833
to using a child as a lab rat!

311
00:16:46,916 --> 00:16:48,500
