Suzuha what we were doing.

312
00:16:48,583 --> 00:16:49,625
She was out here with us!

313
00:16:49,708 --> 00:16:50,875
Say what?

314
00:16:50,958 --> 00:16:52,208
Is that the truth, honey?

315
00:16:52,291 --> 00:16:53,541
Uh huh, she was out here--

316
00:16:53,625 --> 00:16:55,458
but she definitely
wasn't slacking off!

317
00:16:55,541 --> 00:16:56,666
She wasn't, huh...?!

318
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,875
Why you lazy good-for-nothing!

319
00:16:58,958 --> 00:16:59,958
I'm making a break for it!

320
00:17:00,041 --> 00:17:01,375
What the hell am
I paying you for?!

321
00:17:01,458 --> 00:17:04,250
All ya do is goof off!
Look at this!

322
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:05,750
You haven't even
started on this repair!

323
00:17:05,833 --> 00:17:07,875
I... I won't do it again!

324
00:17:17,541 --> 00:17:19,625
Due to unforeseen circumstances,

325
00:17:19,708 --> 00:17:21,500
