hear me, Assistant...?

329
00:17:36,375 --> 00:17:38,208
You're free to go.

330
00:17:38,291 --> 00:17:39,833
Just doing a little thinking.

331
00:17:39,916 --> 00:17:42,916
Oh yes... You'd rather sit there

332
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,166
and stare at my back than
return to the gilded cage

333
00:17:45,250 --> 00:17:47,333
