Little Miss Moneybags?

334
00:17:47,416 --> 00:17:49,250
Quit calling me
that stupid name.

335
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:51,833
I'm composing a very
important message here...

336
00:17:51,916 --> 00:17:54,666
If you insist on loitering,
