337
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:57,541
brain-starved moaning
to a minimum, Zombie.

338
00:17:59,291 --> 00:18:02,333
Oh goody. We're back to
my least favorite nickname.

339
00:18:14,583 --> 00:18:15,750
You're like a schoolgirl,

340
00:18:15,833 --> 00:18:18,958
