boy to write back.

341
00:18:19,041 --> 00:18:21,166
Speaking from
experience, are we...?

342
00:18:23,958 --> 00:18:25,041
What's up, anyway...?

343
00:18:25,125 --> 00:18:27,916
Who're you texting?

344
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,166
