345
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:30,416
Huh?

346
00:18:51,666 --> 00:18:52,666
Daru?

347
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:53,833
What's going on?

348
00:18:53,916 --> 00:18:55,250
Okarin--thank God!

349
00:18:55,333 --> 00:18:58,041
Look, I just realized
I've made a terrible mistake!

350
00:18:58,125 --> 00:19:00,416
What was it...?! Talk, man!

351
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:04,458
It's all... all my fault...

352
00:19:04,541 --> 00:19:06,458
I left my wallet
back at the lab!

353
00:19:06,541 --> 00:19:07,708
What?

354
00:19:07,791 --> 00:19:09,291
Yeah! And Queen May's
shut its doors to me!

355
00:19:09,375 --> 00:19:11,500
I hate to ask, but
could you maybe--?

356
00:19:14,041 --> 00:19:15,916
Too-too-roo! Hi, Okarin.

357
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,000
Oh, hello there, Mayuri.

358
00:19:19,458 --> 00:19:21,083
Daru's gonna be hitting
you up for money...

359
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:23,333
You don't have to give
him anything though, okay?

360
00:19:23,416 --> 00:19:24,666
Okie-dokie...

361
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:27,458
But I called to see if you
were feeling any better.

362
00:19:27,541 --> 00:19:29,791
If you're not, then I give
